nt\npaths. The evolutionary scenario of the occurrence of rotational irregularities\nexplains well many of the observed properties of pulsar rotation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jul 2013 08:18:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2013 08:19:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
