ion data for small k. We have used them to test the\nPatashinski--Pokrovski relation and have found that it holds approximately.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jul 2013 10:25:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-24"}
